edu.jhu.cs.oose.fall2014.shuffletter.iface

Interface ShuffletterTile


  • public interface ShuffletterTile
    A simple interface describing the behavior of a Shuffletter game tile. A correct submission for the first part of this assignment includes a class which implements this interface. This interface is quite simple; it generally acts as a semantic wrapper around characters but also provides functionality for wildcards.

    • Method Summary
